<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَحْسَنُ عَمَلًا}</span> ... أَخْلَصُهُ، وَأَصْوَبُهُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{طِبَاقًا}</span> ... بَعْضُهَا فَوْقَ بَعْضٍ، مِنْ غَيْرِ مُمَاسَّةٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَفَاوُتٍ}</span> ... اخْتِلَافٍ، وَتَبَايُنٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فُطُورٍ}</span> ... شُقُوقٍ، وَصُدُوعٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ثُمَّ ارْجِعِ الْبَصَرَ كَرَّتَيْنِ}</span> ... أَعِدِ النَّظَرَ مَرَّةً بَعْدَ مَرَّةٍ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
