<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{خَاسِئًا}</span> ... ذَلِيلًا صَاغِرًا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حَسِيرٌ}</span> ... مُتْعَبٌ، كَلِيلٌ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رُجُومًا لِّلشَّيَاطِينِ}</span> ... شُهُبًا مُحْرِقَةً لِمُسْتَرِقِي السَّمْعِ مِنَ الشَّيَاطِينِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
